channel.description:
hi guys,

i can ether go to some shitty dentist in tottenham (its a **** hole) or go to my private dentist. The dentist in tottenham only do sedation which is gay but its free, like if you want 1 filling they sedate you. Or i can go to the private dentist and have it numbed (but pay Â£240).
What do you think?
